          li All Internet traffic is <b>securely encrypted</b>, for all apps
          li We use the very secure <b>1024-bit Open SSL</b> encryption standard
          li It works behind firewalls, whether you are at home or work
          li You can use <b>all Internet protocols</b> (torrents, browsing, etc)


